Aspect	OpenAPI 3.0	Swagger 2.0
Version Identifier	openapi: 3.0.0	"swagger": "2.0"
Server Information	servers array	host, basePath, schemes
Request Body	requestBody object	parameters with in: "body"
Response Definitions	content field with media type and schema	Direct schema under response codes
Media Types	Embedded in requestBody and responses	Root-level consumes and produces
Examples	Dedicated example field	Embedded in description as text
